cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with person re-identification, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel metric learning approach, which involves optimization and constraint-based techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves semantic representation, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves security and privacy, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
